game.name: Ellie Ressurection Emergency
game.description:
The beautiful Ice Queen has got sick and her health condition looks pretty serious right now. Only an immediate medical attention can help save her life. Her love has brought the lady to your hospital when she is in the middle of a various serious medical crisis. Without wasting your time anymore, you need to take care of her. Join your patient in the emergency room and be prepared to take the needful steps to perform a CPR by the book in Ellie Ressurection Emergency! 

All her family members have full faith on your medical abilities so feel free to deal with the problem confidently in this brand new girls game. Start the fun by performing the perfect CPR on your patient! Then give her a needful oxygen mask and check if you are able to resuscitate the queen. Keep your eyes on an IV and give your lady all the necessary vitamins once you realize that she has come back to her life in this one of the best interactive doctor games for girls! 

She has got into a big trouble after meeting a big accident and suddenly her heart stopped working properly. Follow all your doctoring skills to bring her back to her normal life and we are pretty sure that she will again start standing on her own feet! Use the defibrillator paddles and both hands to apply the chest compression properly to help her revive shortly! Make sure that she gets the needful medical attention after the resurrection in this doctor simulation game. Have a blast with your friends in our top liked medical simulation games without download!
